  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Cold-water immersion (CWI) is a frequently applied strategy to accelerate post-exercise
      recovery in both recreational as well as professional athletes. However, the effect of
      repeated post-exercise CWI on other recovery strategies remains unclear.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
